response.overview: Here Comes A... Digger! - Kids just dig it! See real Diggers, Dumpers, Dozers, Crushers and more in this fabulous multi award-winning programme for pre-schoolers. Part of a hit series about big machines, this DVD has little ones singing along to the catchy songs and cheering the funny antics of a little bear called 'Ted'. Educational and great fun!
response.tagline: Real Diggers, Dumpers, Dozers, Crushers and more...
response.title: Here Comes A... Digger
